> flush(stderr()); flush(stdout())
> 
> ### Name: pals_params
> ### Title: Create a PALS parameter set
> ### Aliases: pals_params
> 
> ### ** Examples
> 
> p <- pals_params(alpha = 0.9, beta = 0.2, gamma = -10, eta = -10)
> p
<pals_params> (four-parameter model)
  alpha = 0.9, beta = 0.2, gamma = -10, eta = -10
> pals_params(alpha = 0.9, model = "one")
<pals_params> (one-parameter model)
  alpha = 0.9  (pi fixed at 0)
> 
