<pal_events>
  events: 400
  actors: 12
  time:   2000-01-02 to 2016-12-25
  bbox:   lon [4.21, 14.70], lat [4.00, 13.90]
> summary(ev)
<pal_events> summary
  400 events, 12 actors, 2000-01-02 to 2016-12-25
  events per actor: min 16, median 64, max 108
